title: Shunya Kamiya
text:
is a <a href="Japanese%20people">Japanese</a> <a href="Association%20football">football</a> player. He plays for <a href="FC%20Kariya">FC Kariya</a>.
Playing career.
Shunya Kamiya played for <a href="J3%20League">J3 League</a> club; <a href="Fujieda%20MYFC">Fujieda MYFC</a> from 2014 to 2015. In 2016, he moved to <a href="FC%20Kariya">FC Kariya</a>.
